snippet.textDisplay: When "Ami eka hoye boshe Achi" blew up on instagram, I thought probably thats the best part of the song, until I heard him sing  "Na elo na she thake kar bhorshay" and it just blew my mind. This is so far one of my favourite Coke studio bangla track of all time. <3 Bulbuli still tops my chart though. <3 Lots and lots of love from Shillong and the entire Sylheti community of north east India.
